<http://purl.org/dc/terms/format> <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/usageNote> "dcat:mediaType SHOULD be used if the type of the distribution is defined by [IANA](https://www.w3.org/TR/vocab-dcat-3/#bib-iana-media-types)."@en .
<http://purl.org/dc/terms/format> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The file format of the Distribution."@en .
<http://purl.org/dc/terms/format> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "format"@en .
