<http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://www.w3.org/TR/vocab-dcat/> .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "theme"@en .
