<https://w3id.org/emmo/domain/datamodel#datumType> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "Use one of bool, int, float, string. For int and float the number of bits can be added. E.g. int32, float64."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/emmo/domain/datamodel#datumUnit
<https://w3id.org/emmo/domain/datamodel#datumUnit> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
