<https://w3id.org/emmo/domain/datamodel#datumUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "Leave empty if dimensionless."@en .
<https://w3id.org/emmo/domain/datamodel#datumUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "Use standard SI symbols."@en .
