<http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#dm> "http://www.w3.org/TR/2013/REC-prov-dm-20130430/#term-entity"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
