<https://w3id.org/emmo/hume#UnintentionalAgent> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "An agent that is driven by the law of physics rather than the intention to reach a defined objective."@en .
<https://w3id.org/emmo/hume#UnintentionalAgent> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "A catalyst."@en .
<https://w3id.org/emmo/hume#UnintentionalAgent> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "UnintentionalAgent"@en .
